  "texts": [
    "Care was taken to select leaves that did not display any visible signs of damage or pathogen infection.",
    "Because leaf developmental timeline is less well-characterized for non-cacao Theobroma spp.",
    "than it is for T. cacao, we used fully mature leaves.",
    "Leaves were treated with either P. palmivora plugs or control plugs as previously described [36].",
    "Within each tree, we randomized the order in which we processed each species."
  ],
